FBIS3-19419 "drweu052_j_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Mar 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Army Units Deployed in Naples LD1703112694 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1045 GMT 17 Mar 94 LD1703112694 Rome RAI Due Television Network Language: Italian Article Type:BFN [Text] Since this morning units of the Italian army have been stationed in Naples in order to guard courthouses, public offices, and other building considered to be at risk. The decision to use soldiers on military sevice to guard the area around the city of Naples was taken by the Council of Ministers.
